course.subject: SCED
course.name: Advanced Studies in the Teaching and Learning of Chemistry
course.description: Continues to develop students' critical awareness of theoretical and practical issues in chemistry education, their professional attitude and pedagogical content knowledge and competence in facilitating students' chemistry learning.
course.prerequisites: SCED 4210 (prior to 2011-12) and SCED 4410 (prior to 2011-12)
